# 🚀 Verdia Launcher

**Verdia Launcher** is a modern, high-performance launcher built for speed, simplicity, and a clean user experience.

Designed to deliver a smooth and optimized environment, Verdia focuses on performance, minimalism, and reliability.

---

## 🌐 Official Website

👉 https://verdiaclient.live/

---

## ✨ Features

* ⚡ Ultra-fast performance
* 🎨 Clean & modern UI
* 🧠 Optimized resource usage
* 🚀 Smooth launcher experience
* 📦 Easy installation
* 🔄 Future auto-update system

---

## 📥 Download

Get the latest version here:

👉 https://verdiaclient.live/

Or download directly from releases:
👉 https://github.com/kevin12-glitch/verdiaclient/releases

---

## 🖥️ System Requirements

* OS: Windows 10 / 11
* RAM: 4GB+ recommended
* Storage: 200MB free space

---

## 📦 Installation Guide

1. Download the latest version
2. Extract the `.zip` file
3. Run the `.exe` file
4. Launch and enjoy 🚀

---

## ⚠️ Security Notice

Since Verdia Launcher is not yet code-signed:

* Windows may show a warning
* Click **“More info → Run anyway”**

This is normal for new applications.

